OL,3,C'Addiction is addiction - no one sets
OL,4,Cout to be an addict'
OL,6,FEmma Metcalfe is no exception. As a
OL,7,Fformer alcoholic, she has spent years
OL,8,Fin recovery and now runs her own
OL,9,Fcharity to help others living with
OL,10,Faddiction, Hand of Hope NI.
OL,12,FShe is now campaigning for a
OL,13,Fresidential rehabilitation centre in
OL,14,FArmagh and is open about her own
OL,15,Fexperience with addiction.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
