OL,3,C'Addiction is addiction - no one sets
OL,4,Cout to be an addict'
OL,6,FFor Emma, it is this realisation of
OL,7,Fthe tragedy of addiction which has
OL,8,Fmade her so determined to ensure a new
OL,9,Ftreatment centre is set up in Armagh.
OL,11,F"All the grants have started to roll
OL,12,Fin and I'm going to be applying for
OL,13,Feverything and I will get a facility.
OL,14,FPlease God I'll get a facility in
OL,15,FArmagh and when I get one there I'll
OL,16,Fkeep going. I'll keep going because
OL,17,Fevery child, parent, aunt and uncle
OL,18,Fdeserves a chance and a second chance
OL,19,Fat life. A facility...that is my goal."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/6
